data.description: Do not miss the opportunity to own this awesome barndominium! The two story living space is sure to impress with two oversized bedrooms upstairs with large walk-in closets, plenty of space to entertain on the main floor with an open floor plan that leads into the oversized garage. The 30x50 garage space features two extra tall garage doors, 220v outlet, and extra bright LED lighting! The flat 1.5 acres are ready for any ideas you may have! Located less than an hour from the 275 loop!
